history.proof: qsimpl time: 1 use: ind1ParamIsPR. qsimpl time: 1 use: pi1_2IsPR,ind1ParamIsPR. qsimpl time: 1 use: pi1_2IsPR,pi2_2IsPR,ind1ParamIsPR.

exceptions.exn: In environment n : nat n0 : nat e : nat The term "Init.Nat.sub e" has type "nat -> nat" while it is expected to have type "nat".

In environment H : forall f : nat -> nat -> nat -> nat, isPR 3 f -> forall g : nat -> nat, isPR 1 g -> isPR 2 (fun a b : nat => nat_rec (fun _ : nat => nat) (g b) (fun x y : nat => f x y b) a) Unable to unify "isPR 2 (fun a _ : nat => a)" with "isPR 2 Init.Nat.sub".

In environment H1, H : forall f : nat -> nat -> nat -> nat, isPR 3 f -> forall g : nat -> nat, isPR 1 g -> isPR 2 (fun a b : nat => nat_rec (fun _ : nat => nat) (g b) (fun x y : nat => f x y b) a) x : PrimRec 2 H2 : forall c c0 : nat, evalPrimRec 2 x c c0 = c Unable to unify "isPR 2 (fun _ b : nat => b)" with "isPR 2 Init.Nat.sub".

original: apply (ind1ParamIsPR (fun _ _ e => Init.Nat.sub e)). ++ apply pi1_2IsPR. ++ apply pi2_2IsPR.
